snippet.title: Donald Trump Spokesperson: Hillary Clinton Has Not Been Vetted | MSNBC

localized.description:
National spokesperson for Donald Trump’s campaign, Katrina Pierson, reacts to some of the Republican voters’ negative responses to Trump being the likely nominee for the Republican party. She explains why the GOP party needs to unite behind Trump.
